        "summary": "Get Flag Configuration Detail",
        "description": "Get detailed configuration for a specific feature flag. Shows the flag's rules, conditions, rollout percentage, and targeting criteria. Use when someone asks 'what does flag X do', 'flag configuration', or 'how is this flag set up'. Keywords: flag configuration, rollout settings, flag rules.",
